<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

    <meta charset="UTF-8">

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>Blog Post</title>

    <link
        href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        rel="stylesheet">

    <style>

        body {

            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #171A21;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            color: white;

        }

        .navbar {

            z-index: 1000;
            background-color: #171A21 !important;
            padding-left: 20px;
            padding-right: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);

        }

        .navbar-brand {

            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;

        }

        .nav-link {

            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-left: 15px;

        }

        .card {

            border-radius: 15px !important;
            overflow: hidden;
            background-color: #1B2838 !important;

        }

        .card-body {

            background-color: #1B2838;

        }

        .card-title {

            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: bold;

        }

        .card-text {

            line-height: 1.8;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);

        }

        .card-img-top {

            width: 100%;
            height: 500px;
            object-fit: cover;

        }

        .btn {

            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-weight: 500;

        }

        .btn-primary {

            background-color: #1A74E8;
            border: none;

        }

        .btn-success {

            border: none;

        }

        hr {

            border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);

        }

        @media (max-width: 992px) {

            .card-title {

                font-size: 2.3rem;

            }

        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {

            .navbar-brand {

                font-size: 1.5rem;

            }

            .card-title {

                font-size: 2rem;

            }

            .card-img-top {

                height: 350px;

            }

        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {

            .navbar-brand {

                font-size: 1.3rem;

            }

            .card-title {

                font-size: 1.6rem;

            }

            .card-img-top {

                height: 250px;

            }

            .btn {

                width: 100%;
                margin-top: 10px;

            }

        }

    </style>

</head>

<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">

        <div class="container-fluid">

            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/home">
                ByBlogSite
            </a>

            <button
                class="navbar-toggler"
                type="button"
                data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                data-bs-target="#navbarNav">

                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>

            </button>

            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">

                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">

                    <li class="nav-item">

                        <a class="nav-link" href="/home">
                            Home
                        </a>

                    </li>

                    <li class="nav-item">

                        <a class="nav-link active" href="/blog-post">
                            Blog Post
                        </a>

                    </li>

                    <li class="nav-item">

                        <a class="nav-link" href="/post-page">
                            View Posts
                        </a>

                    </li>

                </ul>

            </div>

        </div>

    </nav>

    <div class="container py-5">

        <div class="row justify-content-center">

            <div class="col-lg-10">

                <div class="card bg-dark text-white border-0 shadow-lg">

                    <img
                        src="/images/2.png"
                        class="card-img-top"
                        alt="Blog Image">

                    <div class="card-body p-5">

                        <h1 class="card-title mb-4">
                            Starting Portfolio Project 5
                        </h1>

                        <p class="text-secondary">

                            Author: Michael Clark

                            <br>

                            Date: May 12, 2026

                        </p>

                        <hr>

                        <p class="card-text mt-4">

                            Welcome to my development blog.
                            This website is where I post project updates,
                            coding progress, development ideas,
                            and ongoing work related to software engineering,
                            web development, and creative technology.

                        </p>

                        <p class="card-text">

                            This blog will continue expanding over time
                            with new features, design improvements,
                            database functionality, and interactive systems
                            built using modern web technologies.

                        </p>

                        <p class="card-text">

                            Feel free to explore the site and view
                            future project updates and posts as development
                            continues.

                        </p>

                        <div class="mt-4">

                            <a href="/home" class="btn btn-primary">
                                Back To Home
                            </a>

                            <a href="/post-page" class="btn btn-success ms-2">
                                View Posts
                            </a>

                        </div>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

    <script
        src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js">
    </script>

</body>

</html>